    "For example, for historical monthly mean temperatures, part of the request to the LLM will look like this:",
    "Current mean monthly temperature for each month:",
    "8.58 11.205 15.184 19.388 25.592 31.53 34.645 33.809 28.966 21.668 13.972 9.394",
    "The completed prompt is then sent to the LLM.",
    "ClimSight is currently quite basic: it gathers only limited information related to the place of interest; it only uses results of one climate model simulation with relatively low spatial tion; and it does not take into account uncertainty estimates."
